									<h2>The Fish That Gave Too Much</h2>
									<h3>The Italian fish sauce—<em>colatura—</em>is made from anchovies and literally adds the Mediterranean into the famously healthy Mediterranean diet. So many good things, however, have a downside.</h3>
									<p class="insidepagethumbinfodate">Jul 24, 2018 | 3,100 words, about 16 minutes</p>
